## 6. Practical Examples

### Microservices.io Saga (Eventuate Framework)

```java
// Eventuate Tram Saga implementation
public class CreateOrderSaga implements SimpleSaga<CreateOrderSagaData> {

    private SagaDefinition<CreateOrderSagaData> sagaDefinition = 
        step()
            .invokeParticipant(this::createOrder)
            .withCompensation(this::rejectOrder)
        .step()
            .invokeParticipant(this::reserveCredit)
            .withCompensation(this::releaseCredit)
        .step()
            .invokeParticipant(this::approveOrder)
        .build();

    private void createOrder(CreateOrderSagaData data) {
        orderService.create(data.getOrderDetails());
    }

    private void rejectOrder(CreateOrderSagaData data) {
        orderService.reject(data.getOrderId());
    }

    // ... other participants
}
```

