## ⚠️ Critical Gaps Identified

| Gap | Impact | Mitigation |
|-----|--------|------------|
| **No standard agent compensation** | Each system builds custom | Adopt Temporal/Step Functions patterns |
| **LLM non-determinism** | Replay produces different results | Checkpoint before external calls |
| **External API undo** | Many APIs don't support rollback | Design idempotent operations, use transactions |
| **Compensation timeout** | Undo itself may fail | Nested compensations with dead-letter queue |

